{
  "id": "adv_main_02_02_05",
  "title": "東京編1章10話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫ですか、天動さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you okay‚ Tendo-san?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君！\n早く、救急車呼ばなきゃ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}!\nWe need to call an ambulance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.183333357175191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あの！\n呼ばなくて大丈夫ですから！　落ち着いて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry‚\nThere’s no need! Please calm down…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.716666690508522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "お、落ち着いてなんていられませんわ！\nだって、目の前で……気を失って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but we cannot possibly calm down!\nNot when she fainted… before our very eyes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.883333357175186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、気を失ってるっていうか……\nとりあえず、よく見て下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ she didn’t exactly faint.\nTake a close look at her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.51666669050852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "…………すぅ……すぅ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Zzz… Zzz…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.11666669050852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　もしかして……寝てるだけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….Eh? Is she just… sleeping?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.320498840014135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 36.095782176653536
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです。お騒がせしてすみません\n瑠依ちゃん、急にスイッチ切れることがあって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. Sorry we startled you.\nRui-san suddenly shuts off sometimes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.19578217665355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "体力が空になると、突然寝落ちしちゃうんですよ\nこうなると、しばらくは起きません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When she runs out of stamina‚ she’ll suddenly fall asleep.\nIt takes her a while to wake up when she’s like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.32911550998687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "今日はすみれちゃんが膝枕する日みたいやな\nちょっと羨ましいわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looks like it’s your turn to be her pillow today‚ Sumire-chan.\nI’m a little jealous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.09578230381012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "うう……身動き取れなくなるから\nせめて「寝落ちしそう」ぐらいは言って欲しかったなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… I’m stuck in this position‚ I guess.\nWish she’d at least give us a warning before she falls asleep.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6124489068985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "……良かったですわ……\n急にフッと倒れるんですもの……ビックリしましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What a relief.\nShe just collapsed out of nowhere. I was most frightened.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.31244890689851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "体力が空……てことは、相当疲れてたのね\n歓迎会、今日じゃない方が良かったかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her stamina ran out‚ you said? She must have really been exhausted.\nMaybe we shouldn’t have scheduled the welcome party for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.91244890689849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "それは違いますよ、佐伯さん\nむしろ、今日開いてくれたから……だと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ Saeki-san.\nI think it’s the best choice to threw us a welcome party today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.81244890689851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "知っての通り、瑠依ちゃんはとにかく努力の鬼やから\n毎日フルスロットルで練習してます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As you know‚ Rui-san is the queen of workaholics.\nSo she practices every day at full throttle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.11244890689852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ちまたでは天才なんて言われてるけど、それはちゃう\n瑠依ちゃんは、人の何倍も努力してるだけなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Most people call her a genius… but they’ve got it all wrong.\nRui-san simply works much harder than the average person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.44578224023188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "……前に、ダンスシューズ、見せてもらいましたよね\n新しくしても、一週間でボロボロに……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We did get a look at her dance shoes once.\nIt was a new pair‚ but it was in tatters after a week.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.97911557356524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 110.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "でも多分、ここ数日はそれだけとちゃいますね\nこう見えて、ずぅっと思い悩んでたみたいやから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I don’t think that’s what she did these past few days.\nShe may look strong‚ but she’s been bottling up all her worries.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.37911557356522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロを……解雇されちゃったから……ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because Van Productions… let her go?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.37911557356522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "それも、社長であり……実のお父さんでもある\n朝倉さんから、直接……だもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And what’s more‚ the company president… who’s also her father…\nKyoichi Asakura did it directly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.3830159743627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "そのことでいろいろ悩んじゃって\nあんまり夜、寝られてなかったんじゃないかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that made her worry about a lot of things‚\nand I don’t think she was sleeping much at night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.554036418597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "本人は顔に出さないようにしてましたけど……\nずっと一緒に活動してると、分かっちゃいますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though she never lets it show‚\nwhen you’ve been working with her as long as we have‚ you just know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.75403641859717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "せやけど、こうして星見プロさんが\nうちらを迎え入れてくれた。さらには歓迎会まで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Hoshimi Productions has been so welcoming.\nYou even threw us a welcome party.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.92070308526377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "それできっと\n緊張の糸が切れちゃったのかもしれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That may have loosened\nthe tension building up inside of her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.54403647581756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "だと思います。けど……それでも、普段は人前で\nこんな姿を見せること、ないんですけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s what I think. But still… she usually wouldn’t\nlet herself be seen like this in front of other people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.9773698091508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "それだけ瑠依ちゃんは、星見プロのみなさんと\n一緒にいられて……受け入れてくれて安心したんやろね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That just goes to show that being with you girls at Hoshimi Productions\nand being accepted by you all… has really relieved her worries.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.67736980915078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "せやから、うちらからも改めて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ once again…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.02767548319233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんを……私達の家族を助けてくれて\n本当にありがとうございました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for helping Rui-chan… for helping our family.\nWe appreciate it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.9050449823987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_05-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "この借りは、これから仕事でしっかり\n返していくので……ひとつ、よろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We promise we’ll repay you with our hard work.\nWe look forward to working with you all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.60504498239877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
